      <title>德国游说 Northvolt 建立另一家大型电池工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/germany-lobbies-northvolt-for-another-massive-battery-factory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为柏林持续吸引绿色投资的努力之一，德国正在推动瑞典电池制造商 Northvolt AB 在该国北部建造第二家大型工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/germany-lobbies-northvolt-for-another-massive-battery-factory</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:38:49 GMT</pubDate>
