    <item>
      <title>AI 公司计划为搭载 Nvidia 芯片的服务器设立私人信贷基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/ai-firm-plans-private-credit-fund-for-servers-with-nvidia-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家英国人工智能初创公司计划推出私人信贷基金，购买配备高性能 Nvidia Corp. 芯片的服务器，供亚洲公司使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/ai-firm-plans-private-credit-fund-for-servers-with-nvidia-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:02:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利电信首席执行官称电网交易让公司有空间进行未来的并购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/telecom-italia-ceo-says-network-deal-frees-firm-for-future-m-a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利电信公司 (Telecom Italia SpA) 完成具有里程碑意义的价值 220 亿欧元（238 亿美元）的网络出售后，将为新的交易做好准备，此举旨在让该运营商摆脱数十亿欧元的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/telecom-italia-ceo-says-network-deal-frees-firm-for-future-m-a</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:42:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管信用损失准备金大幅增加，Monzo 仍首次实现盈利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/monzo-makes-first-profit-even-as-credit-losses-soar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒙佐银行有限公司 (Monzo Bank Ltd.) 去年营收增长一倍以上，报告首次实现年度盈利，但其计提的不良贷款拨备超过贷款账簿的十分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/monzo-makes-first-profit-even-as-credit-losses-soar</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:09:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国大城市房地产市场在放松管制后回暖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/china-s-biggest-cities-see-housing-market-pick-up-after-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周末，中国两个最大城市放松房地产限制后购房者信心出现改善，这是数月来陷入困境的房地产行业首次出现的积极信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/china-s-biggest-cities-see-housing-market-pick-up-after-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 07:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PC 制造商 Raspberry Pi 及其支持者在英国罕见 IPO 中寻求 1.57 亿英镑融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/pc-maker-raspberry-pi-backers-seek-157-million-in-rare-uk-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国个人电脑制造商 Raspberry Pi 及其股东希望通过在伦敦首次公开募股筹集 1.57 亿英镑（2 亿美元），这为金融中心的科技上​​市带来了一线希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/pc-maker-raspberry-pi-backers-seek-157-million-in-rare-uk-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 07:00:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
