      <title>高通称笔记本电脑用户将告别电源模块</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/qualcomm-says-laptop-users-will-leave-power-bricks-behind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高通公司表示，采用其新芯片的笔记本电脑用户将可以随心所欲地使用电脑，而不必担心电池耗尽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/qualcomm-says-laptop-users-will-leave-power-bricks-behind</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 06:36:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，黑石集团正在考虑出售 Alinamin Pharmaceutical</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/blackstone-is-said-to-consider-sale-of-1-9-billion-alinamin-pharmaceutical</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，黑石公司正在考虑出售日本消费者保健公司 Alinamin Pharmaceutical Co.，该公司原为武田药品工业株式会社旗下子公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/blackstone-is-said-to-consider-sale-of-1-9-billion-alinamin-pharmaceutical</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 06:30:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>吉尔·波斯特 (Gill Post) 表示押注 1.16 亿美元，GameStop 股价翻倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/gamestop-s-meme-moment-returns-again-with-gill-s-reddit-post</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在引发 2021 年 meme-stock 狂热的 Reddit 账户发布了其在该游戏零售商的 1.16 亿美元持仓后，GameStop Corp. 的股价上涨了一倍多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/gamestop-s-meme-moment-returns-again-with-gill-s-reddit-post</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 03:10:44 GMT</pubDate>
